1819218 THE CONSUMER PROTECTION (AMENDMENT) ACT, 2002
ACT NO. 62 OF 2002 [ 17th December, 2002.]
An Act further to amend the Consumer Protection Act, 1986.
BE it enacted by Parliament in the Fifty- third Year of the Republic of India as follows:-
115701 1 Short title and commencement.-
1446446 1This Act may be called the Consumer Protection (Amendment) Act, 2002.
1235151 2It shall come into force on such date as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint.
